{"id":910304,"date":[{"year":1993,"month":6,"day":13}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"中外文摘","special_issue":"中外文摘","column":"","genre":"","count":"137","ytitle":"","mtitle":"你会送花吗?","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在社交活动中，越来越多的人以送花为礼，以下表述送花的含意或许对您有帮助:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红玫瑰——我爱你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"康乃馨——母亲/温馨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火凤凰——真心不变；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百合花——事业顺利；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毋忘我——永远不忘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱丽斯——浪漫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菊花——长寿/高洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰花——优雅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堂鸟——高贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郁金香——亲密。"}]}